<plot>Eiryo Waga(Nakai Masahiro) is a famous pianist hiding a dark past. A man from Waga's childhood appears before him after one of his performances and to prevent his secrets from being revealed, Waga murders him in cold blood. While leaving the scene Waga bumps into Naruse Asami(Matsuyuki Yasuko) but flees before she can properly identify him. Detective Imanishi(Ken Watanabe) and his partner are sent to the scene and thus begins a murder mystery with Waga trying to elude the detectives while trying to come to grips with his own demons at the same time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?521415</url></doc>
